whatly (6.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rebrand WhatSie -> Whatly, with a new teal identity.
  * Multiple WhatsApp accounts (separate windows or tabs in one window).
  * Chat themes, chat wallpaper, custom CSS and a five-level privacy blur.
  * Working spell checker, checking several languages at once.
  * Monochrome tray option, connection-status indicator, follow system theme.
  * Native Windows 10+ support and many bug fixes.
  * Automatic data migration from the previous WhatSie install.
  * See CHANGELOG.md for the full list.

